headline: M&T Bank Awarded for Its Commitment to Serving Small-Business and Middle-Market Customers
summary: M&T Bank (NYSE:MTB) has been recognized by Crisil Coalition Greenwich as Best Bank for its small-business customer service and middle-market customer satisfaction in the US.
